00:35:25.630 --> 00:35:27.960
Gusto kong maging isang mas mahusay na bersyon ng aking sarili.

00:35:29.190 --> 00:35:30.320
Young Master Fugui,

00:35:30.400 --> 00:35:30.770
maghiwalay tayo ng landas dito.

